45
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:14,680
This is my younger sister, Baozhu.

46
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,920
Greetings, Ms. Song.

47
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,760
If it isn't Lady Ying.

48
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:19,960
Greetings.

49
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:21,480
So glad to have you here.

50
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,080
I've already heard

51
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,360
