for such a fine lady.

54
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:38,480
He was getting betrothed?

55
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,080
Of course.

56
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:43,120
A bunch of matchmakers came and went,

57
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,600
