61
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:04,560
- Mr. Wen.
- Mr. Wen.

62
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,120
Mr. Wen.

63
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,920
Look at mine.

64
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:10,120
Isn't it beautiful?

65
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,600
This is mine.

66
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:13,640
Take another look at mine.

67
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,280
Ms. Chen.

68
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,640
Glad to finally meet you.

69
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:19,320
You are indeed

70
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,440
true to your name.

71
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,640
This time it's indeed better.

72
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:33,480
Right?

73
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:34,840
- Ms. Chen.
- Ms. Chen,

74
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,160
join us for a drink.

75
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,160
Why are you here?

76
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:55,800
You aren't invited.

77
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,880
You've been strutting all over the city.

78
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:02,920
I'm worried about your safety.

79
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,880
I'm perfectly fine.

80
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,880
And I just met many young gentlemen.

81
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,040
Gentlemen?

82
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:17,320
These are all wastrels,

83
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,520
seeking pleasure all day long.

84
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:21,400
Don't fall for their tricks.

85
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:26,440
I heard you've met
a bunch of matchmakers.

86
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,640
Am I not even allowed
to make new friends?

87
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,520
What do you say, Mr. Wen?

88
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:35,600
Are you

89
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:36,800
jealous?

90
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:43,280
What else can I do

91
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,880
other than reject them?

92
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:54,480
I've said it before,

93
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,680
you've always been

94
