for any woman all these years.

99
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,400
No one knows him

100
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,520
better than I do.

101
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,840
He has suffered a lot

102
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:01,360
