103
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,560
Suffered?

104
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,040
He...

105
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:26,360
Mr. Wen.

106
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:28,240
Why are you doing this to yourself?

107
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:29,920
Just apologize to His Majesty

108
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,720
and marry his younger sister.

109
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,280
Wouldn't that be great to join

110
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:34,200
