117
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,400
I will only

118
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,720
marry one woman,

119
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,680
and that's

120
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,520
Baoyin.

121
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:08,960
Hey!

122
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,360
Mr. Wen?

123
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,080
Mr. Wen!

124
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,360
Mr. Wen!

125
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,640
Someone!

126
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,840
Go find the imperial physician!

127
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:48,920
Su nearly froze to death.

128
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,520
Father even had someone make a coffin.

129
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:53,280
After five days and nights,

130
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,400
the old ginseng His Majesty bestowed us

131
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:56,800
saved his life in the end.

132
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:06,200
How could he disobey His Majesty?

133
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,760
He insisted on marrying

134
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:13,120
no one but you,
in case you should return.

135
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:14,720
If he were to marry,

136
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,720
you would be heartbroken.

137
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:25,520
Anyone can see he's still

138
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,680
deeply in love with you.

139
00:08:34,484 --> 00:08:40,180
♪In a dreamlike haze,
our joys and sorrows blend♪

140
00:08:40,180 --> 00:08:43,924
♪When the glory's gone,
this love will never end♪

141
00:08:45,492 --> 00:08:50,016
