150
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:23,760
then I accept.

151
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,720
I just want you to know

152
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,280
(that you have been)

153
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,400
(the only one)

154
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:34,120
(I wish to marry.)

155
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:37,440
(Since you haven't married,)

156
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:40,600
have you ever thought
about me all these years?

157
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,320
I've said it before,

158
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,320
you've always been

159
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,880
the only one I wish to marry.

160
00:09:51,316 --> 00:09:56,110
♪No matter how brief our time,
we hold on tight♪

161
00:09:56,205 --> 00:09:58,272
♪With you, my heart is complete♪

162
00:09:58,272 --> 00:10:01,632
(Su)

163
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:04,480
(Did I make a wrong decision
five years ago?)

164
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:07,080
(I thought he could)

165
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,360
(marry someone of equal standing,)

166
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,960
(the one who could)

167
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:13,640
(help him gain a foothold in the court.)

168
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:16,960
(But I never expected
he would be so stubborn.)

169
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:19,600
(I should have known)

170
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,080
(this is just how he is.)

171
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,800
